<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 14:07:15 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>在有关人质交易的报道中，以色列消息人士称，与哈马斯存在重大分歧，谈判可能会拖延</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-24/ty-article/israeli-sources-differences-with-hamas-on-hostage-deal-significant-talks-may-last-long/0000018d-3b53-d3a5-afdf-7f77277d0000</link><description>报道显示，以色列和哈马斯广泛同意在为期一个月的停火期间进行人质囚犯交换。然而，哈马斯拒绝在没有承诺永久停止的情况下谈论细节，并将人质视为维持加沙平静和保护领导人生命的最重要杠杆。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 12:51:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-24/ty-article/israeli-sources-differences-with-hamas-on-hostage-deal-significant-talks-may-last-long/0000018d-3b53-d3a5-afdf-7f77277d0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡的利库德集团部长和极右翼议员将出席以色列“加沙重新安置”会议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-24/ty-article/netanyahus-likud-ministers-far-right-mks-to-attend-gaza-resettlment-confab/0000018d-3b1e-d35c-a39f-bb5e38070000</link><description>几名以色列议员将于下周日参加在耶路撒冷举行的“胜利会议”，他们声称占领和重新安置加沙地带前以色列定居点是“唯一能带来安全的事情”</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 12:41:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-24/ty-article/netanyahus-likud-ministers-far-right-mks-to-attend-gaza-resettlment-confab/0000018d-3b1e-d35c-a39f-bb5e38070000</guid></item><item><title>现在不要向以色列人询问加沙巴勒斯坦人的伤亡情况</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-24/ty-article/.premium/dont-ask-israelis-right-now-about-palestinian-casualties-in-gaza/0000018d-3770-d32b-adcf-f77227570000</link><description>最近对以色列人和巴勒斯坦人的民意调查得出了惨淡、令人痛苦的结果 — — 这就是为什么领导人，而不是他们破碎的人民，需要提供摆脱这场灾难的出路。但内塔尼亚胡提供的不是领导力，而是黑暗、冰冷的空虚</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 12:21:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-24/ty-article/.premium/dont-ask-israelis-right-now-about-palestinian-casualties-in-gaza/0000018d-3770-d32b-adcf-f77227570000</guid></item><item><title>罕见地点：犹太以色列建筑工人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-24/ty-article-magazine/.premium/a-rare-site-jewish-israeli-construction-workers/0000018d-3b2f-d3a5-afdf-7f3fef790000</link><description>随着以色列建筑业努力取代巴勒斯坦和外国工人，特拉维夫的一个工地找到了雇用最近退役士兵的解决方案</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 12:14:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-24/ty-article-magazine/.premium/a-rare-site-jewish-israeli-construction-workers/0000018d-3b2f-d3a5-afdf-7f3fef790000</guid></item><item><title>以色列高等法院命令耶路撒冷在安息日保持公共泳池开放</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-24/ty-article/.premium/israeli-high-court-orders-jerusalem-to-keep-public-pool-open-on-shabbat/0000018d-3b1e-d3a5-afdf-7f3f07570000</link><description>该裁决命令当地社区管理部门遵守耶路撒冷的现状，即宗教与世俗混合社区的公共泳池每周运营 7 天。一位副市长表示，耶路撒冷自由派屈服于宗教胁迫的日子已经结束了</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 12:13:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-24/ty-article/.premium/israeli-high-court-orders-jerusalem-to-keep-public-pool-open-on-shabbat/0000018d-3b1e-d3a5-afdf-7f3f07570000</guid></item><item><title>学生抗议批评以色列军队的教师复职，阻止他重返教学岗位</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-24/ty-article/.premium/students-demonstrations-against-teacher-who-criticized-idf-prevent-his-return-to-teaching/0000018d-3aa0-d3a5-afdf-7fb799bb0000</link><description>市政府声称，学生对梅厄·巴鲁钦 (Meir Baruchin) 的抗议扰乱了高中的日常事务，法庭裁决推翻了梅厄·巴鲁钦 (Meir Baruchin) 的开除决定。校长在声明中写道，她无法“保证老师的安全”</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 11:43:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-24/ty-article/.premium/students-demonstrations-against-teacher-who-criticized-idf-prevent-his-return-to-teaching/0000018d-3aa0-d3a5-afdf-7fb799bb0000</guid></item><item><title>“就像俄罗斯一样”：以色列会因其在加沙战争中的行为而被踢出欧洲歌唱大赛吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-24/ty-article-magazine/.premium/was-2023-israels-last-year-at-eurovision-pressures-mount-to-exclude-country-due-to-war/0000018d-3624-dfd3-a3bf-beb5cc060000</link><description>四届冠军以色列不再是赔率制定者的最爱，随着加沙战争的激烈，整个欧洲抵制的呼声越来越高</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 10:22:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-24/ty-article-magazine/.premium/was-2023-israels-last-year-at-eurovision-pressures-mount-to-exclude-country-due-to-war/0000018d-3624-dfd3-a3bf-beb5cc060000</guid></item><item><title>南非媒体报道，国际法院预计将于周五对以色列和加沙的紧急措施做出裁决</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-24/ty-article/report-icj-ruling-on-israel-gaza-emergency-measures-expected-by-friday/0000018d-3ac8-d32b-adcf-feeadd100000</link><description>News24 称，南非政府代表团已抵达海牙等待判决。以色列外交部发言人表示并不知情，正在调查此事</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 09:28:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-24/ty-article/report-icj-ruling-on-israel-gaza-emergency-measures-expected-by-friday/0000018d-3ac8-d32b-adcf-feeadd100000</guid></item><item><title>以色列右翼分子为加沙战争辩护，因为人质的痛苦动摇了公众的支持</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-24/ty-article/.premium/the-desperate-plight-of-israeli-hostages-is-eating-away-at-public-support-for-the-war/0000018d-3820-d523-adfd-3d7e36ba0000</link><description>加沙的血腥行动持续的时间越长，以色列右翼声称军队正在“为解救人质而战”的说法就越不被公众接受。内塔尼亚胡领导的利库德集团的一位内阁部长承认，人质问题最终将迫使我们采取行动。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 04:00:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-24/ty-article/.premium/the-desperate-plight-of-israeli-hostages-is-eating-away-at-public-support-for-the-war/0000018d-3820-d523-adfd-3d7e36ba0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列称人质交易还遥遥无期；哈马斯报告称，过去一天加沙袭击造成至少 210 人死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-24/ty-article-live/israeli-army-will-learn-lessons-from-deadly-khan-yunis-incident-idf-chief-says/0000018d-3976-d523-adfd-3d7e56fd0000</link><description>以色列消息人士称，潜在新人质协议的谈判远未达成协议 ■ 财政部长：“我们不会支持战争长期停顿” ■ 在以色列，英国卡梅伦预计将就加沙援助问题向内塔尼亚胡施压 ■ 美国军事打击两名胡塞武装也门的反舰导弹 ■ 加沙有 21 名士兵丧生，这是 10 月 7 日以来最严重的事件</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 03:19:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-24/ty-article-live/israeli-army-will-learn-lessons-from-deadly-khan-yunis-incident-idf-chief-says/0000018d-3976-d523-adfd-3d7e56fd0000</guid></item><item><title>经过十年的拖延，以色列最高法院裁定苏丹寻求庇护者必须获得临时居民身份</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-23/ty-article/.premium/israels-supreme-court-rules-sudanese-asylum-seekers-be-granted-temporary-resident-status/0000018d-3733-d32b-adcf-f773bdcf0000</link><description>犹太援助组织 HIAS 副主任表示：“我们希望这只是迈向公平和适当庇护制度的第一步……规范临时身份带来的不仅仅是健康保险和社会福利，而是一种感觉安全的</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 19:12:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-23/ty-article/.premium/israels-supreme-court-rules-sudanese-asylum-seekers-be-granted-temporary-resident-status/0000018d-3733-d32b-adcf-f773bdcf0000</guid></item><item><title>据报道，哈马斯拒绝以色列为期两个月的停火提议以换取人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-23/ty-article/hamas-reportedly-rejects-two-month-cease-fire-proposal-by-israel-in-exchange-for-hostages/0000018d-36f9-d6f3-a7af-3fffb8100000</link><description>以色列政府发言人周二发表讲话，没有证实已提出要约，但表示正在努力遣返人质</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 19:10:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-23/ty-article/hamas-reportedly-rejects-two-month-cease-fire-proposal-by-israel-in-exchange-for-hostages/0000018d-36f9-d6f3-a7af-3fffb8100000</guid></item><item><title>加沙的严重伤亡引发以色列公众对停火和潜在人质协议的讨论</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-23/ty-article/.premium/heavy-casualties-in-gaza-spark-israeli-public-discourse-on-cease-fire-hostage-deal/0000018d-371f-d32b-adcf-f77fb7860000</link><description>加沙与哈马斯的战斗开始类似于第二次黎巴嫩战争和第一次黎巴嫩战争期间的安全区 ■ 在没有取得明确和决定性胜利的情况下，以色列选择将重点放在敌人的伤亡人数上</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 17:59:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-23/ty-article/.premium/heavy-casualties-in-gaza-spark-israeli-public-discourse-on-cease-fire-hostage-deal/0000018d-371f-d32b-adcf-f77fb7860000</guid></item><item><title>以色列 2023 年度鸟类比赛获胜者：迷失的花斑丛林聊天</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-23/ty-article/winner-of-israels-bird-of-the-year-2023-contest-a-lost-pied-bush-chat/0000018d-3725-d32b-adcf-f7671da60000</link><description>这只聊天鸟是知更鸟的近亲，它可能来自伊朗，它勇敢地在观鸟者面前炫耀了几个月，而不是躲在同名的灌木丛中</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 17:39:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-23/ty-article/winner-of-israels-bird-of-the-year-2023-contest-a-lost-pied-bush-chat/0000018d-3725-d32b-adcf-f7671da60000</guid></item><item><title>“我们以色列人对美国的依赖比我们想象的要严重得多”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-01-23/ty-article-podcast/we-in-israel-are-far-more-dependent-on-the-u-s-than-we-ever-knew/0000018d-36f2-dbf8-abdf-bef6eeb50000</link><description></description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 17:34:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-01-23/ty-article-podcast/we-in-israel-are-far-more-dependent-on-the-u-s-than-we-ever-knew/0000018d-36f2-dbf8-abdf-bef6eeb50000</guid></item><item><title>以色列在加沙最血腥的一天引发了人们对接下来会发生什么的疑问</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-23/ty-article/.premium/israels-bloodiest-day-in-gaza-raises-questions-over-what-comes-next/0000018d-36ad-d6f3-a7af-3fefd1e90000</link><description>一次事件中 21 名以色列国防军士兵丧生，证明了涉及大量爆炸物的地面行动的危险性。它还对在边境建立缓冲区的优点提出质疑</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 15:19:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-23/ty-article/.premium/israels-bloodiest-day-in-gaza-raises-questions-over-what-comes-next/0000018d-36ad-d6f3-a7af-3fefd1e90000</guid></item><item><title>真主党两周内第二次袭击以色列北部的以色列国防军空军基地</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-23/ty-article/.premium/hezbollah-hits-idf-airbase-in-northern-israel-for-second-time-in-two-weeks/0000018d-368a-dbf8-abdf-bede69f70000</link><description>真主党表示，它发射这些导弹是为了回应以色列暗杀真主党和圣城旅指挥官的事件，并在检测到以色列空军基地存在“漏洞”后；以色列国防军报告“轻微损坏”</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 14:47:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-23/ty-article/.premium/hezbollah-hits-idf-airbase-in-northern-israel-for-second-time-in-two-weeks/0000018d-368a-dbf8-abdf-bede69f70000</guid></item><item><title>“总统不能否决我的投票”：拜登在首次民主党初选中面临加沙考验</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-01-23/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-president-cant-veto-my-vote-biden-faces-gaza-test-in-first-democratic-primary/0000018d-35c2-d6df-adcf-35d3f6580000</link><description>一些活动人士发誓要在周二的新罕布什尔州初选中写下“停火”，以抗议总统乔·拜登对以色列与哈马斯战争的态度。由于党内不和，拜登的名字根本没有出现在选票上</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 13:07:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-01-23/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-president-cant-veto-my-vote-biden-faces-gaza-test-in-first-democratic-primary/0000018d-35c2-d6df-adcf-35d3f6580000</guid></item><item><title>以色列清空了北部地区。现在官员们担心撤离人员在战后不会返回家园</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-23/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israel-emptied-its-north-now-officials-fear-evacuees-wont-return-home-after-the-war/0000018d-35df-d6df-adcf-35df4bb70000</link><description>加沙战争期间，居住在黎巴嫩边境附近的近8万人被疏散或逃离；一项调查显示，只有 60% 的人确定自己想回国</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 13:01:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-23/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israel-emptied-its-north-now-officials-fear-evacuees-wont-return-home-after-the-war/0000018d-35df-d6df-adcf-35df4bb70000</guid></item><item><title>与 10 月 7 日受害者一起工作的顶级精神病学家向以色列发出警告</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-23/ty-article-magazine/.premium/senior-psychiatrist-working-with-october-7-victims-israel-needs-a-prescription-of-hope/0000018d-35d3-db8f-a7df-37f3de210000</link><description>什洛莫·门德洛维奇教授表示，仍然很难估计有多少以色列人会患上创伤后应激障碍（“估计有 60,000 到 600,000 个新病例”）。他解释了为什么团体治疗可能是一场灾难，并建议以色列必须采取哪些措施才能康复</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 12:45:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-23/ty-article-magazine/.premium/senior-psychiatrist-working-with-october-7-victims-israel-needs-a-prescription-of-hope/0000018d-35d3-db8f-a7df-37f3de210000</guid></item></channel></rss>